headline: Can Agilent (A) Turn AI-Driven Diagnostics Into a Lasting Competitive Edge?
summary: In recent days, Agilent Technologies unveiled significant developments, including the launch of its Insight Series Alarm Resolution Systems for airport security, the introduction of Altura Ultra Inert HPLC columns tailored for biotherapeutics applications, and a partnership with Lunit to advance AI-powered companion diagnostics for cancer detection.
